func rootsOfUnity(n int) []complex128 {
	w := make([]complex128, n)
	for i := 0; i < n; i++ {
		angle := math.Pi * float64(2*i) / float64(n)
		w[i] = complex(math.Cos(angle), math.Sin(angle))
	}
	return w
}
